### Get all actors (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/actors

### Get all actors (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/actors?_page=1&_limit=10

### Get actor by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/actors/3

### Create actor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/actors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "New actor",
  "country": "United States of America",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01",
  "death_date": null,
  "photo": null,
  "biography": null
}

### Update actor (full)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/actors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 238,
  "full_name": "Updated actor",
  "country": "United States of America",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01",
  "death_date": "2000-01-01",
  "photo": null,
  "biography": null
}

### Update actor (patch)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/actors/238 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Patched actor",
  "country": "Great Britain (England)"
}

### Delete actor
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/actors/238 HTTP/1.1
